snippet.title: Amber Heard ORDERED To Show PROOF Of $7Million Charity Donations!
snippet.description:
Judge Bruce White has ordered Amber Heard to show proof of her alleged $7million donations to charity and her previous arrest records!
This is a huge win for Johnny Depp.

This is outrageous and Johnny Deserves Justice!!!
